# Grading Rubric Rules — Menu Grading Tool

## Sacred Weights (DO NOT CHANGE without explicit instruction)
| Section | Weight | Full (10pts) | Partial (5pts) | None (0pts) |
|---------|--------|-------------|----------------|-------------|
| NEATNESS: Capitalization/punctuation/spelling | 10 | 0-1 errors | 2-5 errors | >5 errors |
| ORGANIZATION: Variations correctly identified | 10 | 0 errors | 1-3 errors | >3 errors |
| ORGANIZATION: Modifier ordering | 10 | 0 errors | 1-3 sets wrong | >3 or illogical |
| ORGANIZATION: Menu grid/display groups | 10 | All criteria met | 1-2 not met | ≥3 not met |
| ACCURACY: Auto Add to Check | 10 | 0-1 errors | 2-5 errors | >5 errors |
| ACCURACY: Modifier sets correct | 10 | 0-1 errors | 2-3 sets wrong | >3 sets wrong |
| ACCURACY: Items named/no duplicates | 10 | 0-1 errors | 2-3 errors | >3 errors |
| ACCURACY: Correct locations/groups | 10 | 0-1 errors | 2-3 errors | >3 errors |
| THOROUGHNESS: Special instructions followed | 10 | 100% | 75-99% | <75% |
| THOROUGHNESS: Critical thinking | 10 | Evident | Attempted but failed | No effort |
| **TOTAL** | **100** | | | |

## Title Case Rules
- Capitalize first letter of every word EXCEPT: of, with, and, the, a, an, in, on, at, to, for, or, but, nor
- First word always capitalized regardless
- Units abbreviated without spaces: 8oz, 250ml, 5lb

## Auto-Add-to-Check Rules
| Market | Condition | Auto-Add |
|--------|-----------|----------|
| US/EU | Drink, no variations, no modifiers | YES |
| US/EU | Drink with variations or modifiers | NO |
| US/EU | Non-drink item | NO |
| AU | ANY item, no variations, no modifiers | YES |
| AU | ANY item with variations or modifiers | NO |

## Variation Rules
- Variations = mutually exclusive options with DIFFERENT prices
- Order: smallest → largest OR cheapest → most expensive
- Item name must NOT appear in variation name
- If each option has unique description → separate items instead

## Modifier Rules
- Modifiers = optional customizations applied across variations
- Required modifier sets appear FIRST
- Options within sets are ALPHABETIZED
- Context must be included (e.g., "Chocolate Shake" not "Chocolate")
- Nested modifiers used when needed (e.g., Salad → Ranch/Balsamic)
- Pricing must match menu
- Min/max selections must be correct

## Duplicate Rules
- Duplicates ONLY allowed when price/modifiers differ per service
- Must be named accordingly: "Caesar Salad - Lunch", "Caesar Salad - Dinner"
- Multi-location items should NOT be duplicated

## Item Naming Rules
- Must NOT contain the word "or" (split into separate items)
- Must include context (e.g., "Chocolate Shake" not "Chocolate")
